ze: small;\">Note that due to clock shifts around the world, the most suitable time has Berlin/Rome/Norway time at 11pm and Tokyo time at 7am.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Tahoma; direction: ltr; color: #000000; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"layout-grid-mode: line; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">I can set up&nbsp;dummy meetings&nbsp;as well&nbsp;if anyone needs to test the&nbsp;GoToMeeting\'s</span><a></a><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> system&nbsp;out.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Tahoma; direction: ltr; color: #000000; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"layout-grid-mode: line; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman; font-size: small;\">The actual GoToMeeting invitation and meeting documents will be sent/available closer to the meeting.&nbsp; Please send any items for the agenda up until the end of November.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Tahoma; direction: ltr; color: #000000; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"layout-grid-mode: line; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Thanks, Mike.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Tahoma; direction: ltr; color: #000000; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">\r\n<div><span style=\"layout-grid-mode: line; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"color: #323232; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" lang=\"EN\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</span>These are the corresponding times for your meeting:\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\">\r\n<table class=\"xpad border2\" border=\"0\">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr class=\"head\">\r\n<th>Location</th><th class=\"sep\">Local time</th><th class=\"sep\">Time zone</th><th class=\"sep\">UTC offset</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tb